-    /**
-     * Adds or updates an item in the series and sends a
-     * {@link SeriesChangeEvent} to all registered listeners.
-     *
-     * @param x  the x-value.
-     * @param y  the y-value.
-     *
-     * @return The item that was overwritten, if any.
